---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { useTranslation } from '../../i18n';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import activitats_portada from '../../assets/rock-climbing.jpg';

const t = useTranslation('es');
---

<Layout 
  lang="es"
  title="Actividades - Caltrucafort"
  description={t('activities.description')}
>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <Image 
        src={activitats_portada} 
        alt="Actividades - Escalada"
        width={1920}
        height={1080}
        class="hero-image"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>{t('activities.title')}</h1>
        <p>{t('activities.subtitle')}</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Description Section -->
    <section class="section-light text-center mb-2xl">
      <p class="description-text">{t('activities.description')}</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Activities Section -->
    <section class="py-xl activities-main">
      <div class="seccion-actividad">
        <div class="texto-bloque">
          <p>La comarca del <strong>Priorat</strong> es la tierra por excelencia del vino y del aceite de oliva. Si os interesa el turismo gastronómico o el enoturismo, estáis en el lugar idóneo para descubrir bodegas locales y catas únicas.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="imagen-bloque">
          <img src="https://MyBlog-c8ewh8hmm2.live-website.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/wines-g169915ad1_1280.jpg">
        </div>

        <div class="amazon-card-mini">
          <span>RECOMENDACIÓN</span>
          <img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/613odjueqPL._AC_SY741_.jpg" alt="Vino Priorat">
          <h4>Clos Mogador 2021</h4>
          <a href="https://amzn.to/4qs7Z9f" target="_blank" class="btn-amazon" style="background: #FF9900; color: black; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; display: block;">Ver en Amazon</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="seccion-actividad seccion-destacada">
        <div class="texto-bloque">
          <p><strong>Margalef</strong>, a solo 4 km, es una referencia mundial para la <strong>escalada</strong>. Sus paredes de conglomerado atraen a escaladores de todo el planeta. Un entorno salvaje perfecto para la aventura.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="imagen-bloque">
          <img src="https://MyBlog-c8ewh8hmm2.live-website.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/rappelling-g1aa8b4681_1280.jpg">
        </div>

        <div class="amazon-card-mini">
          <span>EQUIPACIÓN</span>
          <img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61KHFeq-mPL._AC_UL320_.jpg" alt="Magnesio Escalada">
          <h4>Pack Magnesio y Accesorios Escalada</h4>
          <a href="https://amzn.to/4sMeyF6" target="_blank" class="btn-amazon" style="background: #FF9900; color: black; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; display: block;">Ver en Amazon</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <section class="py-xl text-center cta-section">
      <h2 class="mb-lg">¿Quieres reservar una actividad?</h2>
      <a href="/es/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contactar Ahora</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Description Text Styling */
  .description-text {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
  }

  /* Activities Main Section */
  .activities-main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  /* Activity Cards */
  .seccion-actividad {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    border-radius: 15px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .seccion-actividad:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .seccion-destacada {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5 0%, #fff 100%);
  }

  /* Text Block */
  .texto-bloque {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #555;
  }

  .texto-bloque p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .texto-bloque strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Image Block */
  .imagen-bloque img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .imagen-bloque img:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
  }

  /* Amazon Card */
  .amazon-card-mini {
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .amazon-card-mini:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .amazon-card-mini span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .amazon-card-mini img {
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin: 1rem auto;
  }

  .amazon-card-mini h4 {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
  }

  .btn-amazon {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    background: #FF9900;
    color: black;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid #FF9900;
  }

  .btn-amazon:hover {
    background: #e68900;
    border-color: #e68900;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 153, 0, 0.3);
  }

  /* Button Styling */
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 48px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(204, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: #333;
  }

  /* Removed unused styles */
</style>
